                </a>
                </div>
				<br>
				<br>
				<p class="lead">
					<span i18n:translate="work_based_on">This work is part of the graduate school on</span> <a href="http://www.fortschrittskolleg.de/" target="_blank"><span i18n:translate="online_participation">Online-Participation</span></a>.
					<span i18n:translate="funded_by">It is funded by the</span> <a href="http://www.wissenschaft.nrw.de/forschung/fortschritt-nrw/inter-und-transdisziplinaere-forschung/fortschrittskolleg-online-partizipation/" target="_blank"><span i18n:translate="ministry_of_innovation">Ministry of Innovation, Science and Research in North Rhine-Westphalia</span></a>.
				</p>
